title: Ukrainian military had 76 combat engagements with Russian forces near Terny of Donetsk region, Bila Hora of Donetsk region, B...
content: Ukrainian military had 76 combat engagements with Russian forces near Terny of Donetsk region, Bila Hora of Donetsk region, Berdychi, Tonenke, Pervomayske, Nevelske, Semenivka and Orlivka, Heorhiyivka, Novomykhaylivka, Prechystivka and Krasnohorivka of Donetsk region, Huliaipole, Malynivka and Robotyne, at the eastern bank of Dnipro river in Kherson region, - General Staff of Armed Forces of Ukraine says in the evening report
